   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The battery temperature sensor can either be connected at the controller
or in the terminal section.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">In systems with internal batteries the temperature sensor is already
installed in the factory and connected to the controller.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">For external batteries the temperature sensor must be connected
at the terminal section to a terminal, for the reference designator
and more details see the <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Drawings</i>.</p>
      <note class="- topic/note ">After the batteries are installed the position of the temperature
sensor should be checked. It is recommended to place the temperature
sensor close to a battery cell in the middle of the battery bank.</note>
   </conbody>
